  <!-- Who can join? -->
  <section id="eligibility" class="mb-4 mt-5">
      <h2 class="h3 mb-3 border-bottom pb-2 ">Who can join?</h2>
      <p>
          All children between the ages of 9-15 are welcome to join the Ombu Hub! Whether you're a newbie or a tech savvy, there's a place for you here.
      </p>

      <h2 class="h3 mb-3 border-bottom pb-2 ">When and how?</h2>
      <p>
          The workshop will be online and will take place on <%= @course.when %> - Berlin/Amsterdam/Madrid Time CET UTC +1.
      </p>

      <h2 class="h3 mb-3 border-bottom pb-2 ">What is needed?</h2>
      <p>
        <ul>
          <li>Age between 9 and 15 years old. 😀</li>
          <li>Computer with connection to the internet. 💻</li>
          <li>Good level of English, as the workshop will be held in English. 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿</li>
          <li>Lots of interest to learn and grow.🚀</li>
        </ul>
      </p>
  </section>

    <section id="about-ombuhub" class="mb-4">
      <h2 class="h3 mb-3 border-bottom pb-2 ">What is Ombu Hub?</h2>
      <p>
          Ombu Hub is a kid academy designed specifically for the young minds. We believe every child has the potential to craft wonders, and with the power of Robotics, Coding and Design, only the sky's the limit! Dive into a world where coding meets creation.
      </p>
  </section>


  <!-- What do we offer? -->
  <section id="offerings" class="mb-4">
      <h2 class="h3 mb-3 border-bottom pb-2 ">What do we offer in our school?</h2>
      <ul class="">
          <li></i> Interactive Sessions: Learn Robotics, 3D Printing, and more concepts through fun and engaging methods.</li>
          <li></i> Hands-on Projects: Bring your ideas to life with practical projects.</li>
          <li></i> Instructors: Passionate experts molding the next generation.</li>
          <li></i> Collaborative Learning: Team up with other Ombues and embark on tech adventures.</li>
      </ul>
  </section>


